      "to_id": "cec50b17:25",
      "content": "Rename the MCP tool `start_activity` to `start_task` in the source code and all template/protocol docs.\n\n**Work inside:** `.synapse/worktrees/developer-25-rename-start-activity`\nCommit your changes to that branch. Do not push.\n\n---\n\n**Files to change:**\n\n**`src/mcp-server.ts`** — rename the tool and all references to it:\n- Line 271: `name: 'start_activity'` → `name: 'start_task'`\n- Line 299: update description text — `'Mark a task as done. Pass the activity_id from start_task, ...'`\n- Line 307: `'The id returned by start_activity.'` → `'The id returned by start_task.'`\n- Line 330: `'Use this instead of separate send_message + start_activity ...'` → `'... + start_task ...'`\n- Line 582: `if (name === 'start_activity')` → `if (name === 'start_task')`\n\n**Template/protocol docs** (also inside the worktree at `templates/` and `.synapse/`):\nReplace ALL occurrences of `start_activity` with `start_task` in:\n- `templates/SYNAPSE.md`\n- `templates/SYNAPSE-orchestrator.md`\n- `templates/SYNAPSE-worker.md`\n- `.synapse/SYNAPSE.md`\n- `.synapse/SYNAPSE-orchestrator.md`\n- `.synapse/SYNAPSE-worker.md`\n\nNote: `finish_activity` stays as-is — only `start_activity` is being renamed.\n\n**Build:** `npm run build` must pass. Commit all changes in one commit. Report DONE to cec50b17:0.",
